You are eligible for Loan application if:
(1) you are of the legal age under the laws of Cambodia;
(2) you are a full customer information file as per regulatory requirement;
(3) you hold an active Bank Account with the Bank; and
(4) you are a current employee of Royal Group Companies at the time of loan application;
(5) you use the services offered through Bank Account and Wing Bank App before applying for loan.

